flowchart TB
  MCP[MCP system]

  A[Architecture<br/>Exposure, networking, policy path]
  TT[Tool trust<br/>Discovery, provenance, recertification]
  DA[Delegated authority<br/>Credentials, approvals, least privilege]
  CI[Context integrity<br/>Schemas, outputs, metadata, errors]
  CT[Containment + telemetry<br/>Sandboxing, egress, tracing, audit]

  A --> MCP
  TT --> MCP
  DA --> MCP
  CI --> MCP
  CT --> MCP

  Ops[Operational use<br/>Map controls, owners, and tests by plane]
  Why[Why this matters<br/>One incident often crosses multiple planes]

  Ops -.-> A
  Ops -.-> TT
  Why -.-> DA
  Why -.-> CT

